statements: SELECT * FROM WebsiteTraffic;
SELECT VisitorID, PageVisited FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE DeviceType='Mobile';
SELECT PageVisited, VisitDateTime FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE ConversionStatus=TRUE;
SELECT VisitorID, DeviceType, ReferrerPage FROM WebsiteTraffic ORDER BY VisitDateTime DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT DeviceType FROM WebsiteTraffic;
SELECT VisitorID, PageVisited, VisitDateTime FROM WebsiteTraffic ORDER BY VisitDateTime DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT PageVisited, DeviceType FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE ConversionStatus = true
SELECT VisitorID, PageVisited, DeviceType FROM WebsiteTraffic WHERE DeviceType = 'Mobile' ORDER BY VisitorID

SELECT VisitorID, PageVisited, DeviceType, ConversionStatus FROM WebsiteTraffic ORDER BY VisitorID DESC

SELECT * FROM conversions WHERE conversion_type = 'purchase' ORDER BY conversion_timestamp DESC
SELECT * FROM page_views WHERE device_type = 'mobile' AND browser = 'Chrome'
SELECT id, user_id, timestamp FROM page_views WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT user_id, product_id, purchase_amount FROM conversions WHERE purchase_amount > 1000
SELECT * FROM page_views;
SELECT id, user_id, timestamp FROM page_views WHERE browser = 'Chrome';
SELECT page_id, device_type FROM page_views WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_views FROM page_views;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_conversions FROM conversions GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_conversions > 1;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_visitors FROM website_traffic;
SELECT * FROM user_sessions ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT conversion_id, conversion_type FROM conversion_rates WHERE conversion_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT conversion_id, conversion_type FROM conversion_rates WHERE conversion_timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY conversion_timestamp ASC;
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(*) AS page_visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_visited HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY page_visit_count DESC;

SELECT website_traffic.visitor_id, user_sessions.start_time, user_sessions.end_time FROM website_traffic JOIN user_sessions ON website_traffic.visitor_id = user_sessions.visitor_id ORDER BY start_time ASC, end_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_metrics ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, page_url, page_views FROM website_traffic_metrics WHERE page_views > 100 ORDER BY page_views DESC;
SELECT page_url, visitor_ip FROM website_traffic_metrics WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT user_id, username, action FROM user_activity WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-02-28' ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM conversion_rates WHERE conversion_type = 'purchase' AND conversion_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_metrics WHERE page_views > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, visitor_ip, timestamp FROM website_traffic_metrics WHERE page_url LIKE '%homepage%' AND timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_url, visitor_ip, COUNT(visitor_ip) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic_metrics GROUP BY page_url ORDER BY total_visits DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_activity WHERE action = 'login' AND username IN ('user1', 'user2', 'user3') ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(session_id) AS total_sessions FROM user_sessions WHERE end_time IS NOT NULL GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_sessions > 5 ORDER BY total_sessions DESC;

SELECT page_visited, visit_timestamp FROM website_visitors WHERE conversion_goal = true;

SELECT username, email FROM user_accounts WHERE subscription_status = true;
